:::Ripples start to form in the bowl... rolling endlessly... The murmuring water whispers of revelry, the undulating tidal patterns like tiny waves, like this small space has also become a roiling ocean...
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Mission_454050302-->
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' {{Size|36|Ahh absolute bliss! 'Tis the pinnacle of bliss!}}
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' Such long-awaited satisfaction, thank you, my dear! This ambrosia has sobered me up a little... The visage of your reflection is so good-looking that I can't help but get all stirred up...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Thanks for the compliment.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I think I'm very pretty too.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504033206-->
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' Time... How long has passed? Oronyx, you move fast...
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' This starry sky... I see, she still hasn't given up... You are also a fool in this banquet...
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' Dance hard then... indulge hard... waste time hard... Little fishy that wants to swim to tomorrow...
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' When your banquet ends... the absurdity that you will see when you sober up will be the price of buying inebriation...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you even saying?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What the heck are you?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You speak less sense sober than when you're drunk.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504033213-->
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' ...
:::'''Voice of the Tides:''' Ambrosia... Ambrosia...
:::The tide's voice is languid once more, its words fragmented like water splashes &mdash; it seems this basin's desire for liquid is insatiable, an ever-unquenchable patron of ambrosia.
